{"tid":1158703,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今年公司開始請實習 點知做到比人屌死","createTime":"2019-05-17T06:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T14:01:02.000Z","uid":78533,"like":7,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d555fb0cfb3b8b54d63c57ad8ae16bb1396de310","tid":1158703,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細it公司 本身日日番去鳩鳩下又日 老細都叫幾順得人<br />\n點知老細上星期突然話大有個實習聽日會到<br />\n<br />\n咁個個都諗住好啦 有個新人恰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知惡夢咁就黎左 一到步<br />\n23歲男仔 樣衰冇朋友 好似讀書幾叻 <br />\n老細見我地成日話好忙 又係第一次請實習就自己派d 輕ken野<br />\n<br />\n就係咁我地連恰佢既機會都冇 點撚知佢仲話頭醒尾 <br />\n仲將我地平時用黎柒既工作用一半時間就做好<br />\n<br />\n老細就係咁越比越多野佢做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條撚樣又真係識做又做得快<br />\n<br />\n結果我地d野都比佢做撚埋 叫家老細係咁屌我地學生都不如 請咁多人番黎原來得個柒字 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒到叫刻真係唔知點同老細解釋 老細呢家同工個實習去食T   <br />\n仲好似話想出獎金比佢用黎留住佢 <br />\n<br />\n真係屌你老母 唔好比我捉到你痛腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2be0fefaac1d8e35ce954e0d330d6c64b644677","tid":1158703,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"正常23歲都u grad啦 仲做實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0105fcaa32bdbe85e665cf21e474abd89363253c","tid":1158703,"uid":78533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a2be0fefaac1d8e35ce954e0d330d6c64b644677","tid":1158703,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"正常23歲都u grad啦 仲做實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"唔係大學生 好似係d咩文憑課程之